INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (10,1,'2021-04-02 06:23:43','2021-04-02 06:23:43','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The website is a portfolio styled domain tailored towards showcasing the work and achievements of musical artistes, as well as providing users with news of upcoming events and achievements for these respective artistes. On the <strong>home page</strong> of our site, sliders will be used to showcase new/trending albums by various artistes. The information displayed on the home page can be filtered by users to display information on a fixed artistes of their choice. An <strong>About us</strong> page will be used to let new users know what the functionality of the website entails, and what benefits they may withdraw from using our website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The website will possess a <strong>“Music Library”</strong> page that will allow users to view detailed information on all artistes, their albums, their songs, songs they have featured in and their awards won. This ‘Music Library’ page can also be filtered by album/song/artiste to present more precise listings to the user, allowing for a more enjoyable user experience. Our site will have a <strong>“New Releases” </strong>blog page which will be used to post news on song/album releases by various artistes, as well as additional details such as awards won for these songs/albums/artistes. A second blog page, <strong>“Upcoming Events”</strong>, independent of the previously mentioned, will be used for posting news on upcoming events being held by various artistes(these events include concerts/parties for example) and details such as songs to be played during those events will also be posted on this page. Users will be able to filter the 2 previously mentioned blog pages to only view news on specific artistes/genres if desired. Each of the above pages mentioned will also possess a fully functional search bar which allows a user to search for any content across the page / website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About Us','','publish','closed','closed','','about-us','','','2021-04-13 04:22:27','2021-04-13 04:22:27','',0,'http://noted.local/?page_id=10',0,'page','',0);
